Senior Consultant Yvette Filatoff's take on embracing equity as part of this year's International Women's Day theme, #EmbraceEquity.

#IWD

Today's the day we celebrate the impact diversity and inclusion bring not only to our workplaces, but our society and culture.

We are proud to celebrate this year's theme of #EmbraceEquity.

At Webprofits, we recognise the importance of creating a level playing field for everyone and believe that this starts with empowering our people.

We're committed to building a culture that fosters equity and have made a conscious effort to do so. We believe that by creating an environment where everyone feels supported and valued, we can all thrive together.

This International Women's Day, we celebrate the incredible achievements of women around the world and pledge to continue supporting and empowering them every day.

Join us in celebrating International Women's Day and the theme of Embrace Equity. Together, let's create a world where everyone has the opportunity to succeed.

#IWD2023 #EmbraceEquity #InclusionMatters #DiversityandInclusion #WomeninBusiness
